## ğŸ“Š Core Algorithm (30 lines simplified)

```python
def calculate_score(student, alumni):
    score = 0
    
    # University match
    if student['university'] == alumni['university']:
        score += 200
    
    # Industry match
    if student['preferred_industry'] == alumni['industry']:
        score += 160
    
    # Skill matches
    common_skills = len(set(student['skills']) & set(alumni['skills']))
    score += common_skills * 90
    
    # Interest matches
    common_interests = len(set(student['interests']) & set(alumni['interests']))
    score += common_interests * 70
    
    # Mentoring alignment
    mentor_match = len(set(student['looking_for']) & set(alumni['mentoring_areas']))
    score += mentor_match * 50
    
    # Availability bonus
    if alumni['availability'] == 'Available':
        score += 50
    
    return score
```

